n%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnonalcoholic-drinks-to-make-at-home-bartenders-recipes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emocktails%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20realized%20how%20much%20better%20they%20made%20me%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpower-hours-day-in-the-life-successful-business-leaders-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPower%20Hours%3C%2Fa%3E%20series%20gives%20readers%20an%20inside%20look%20at%20how%20powerful%20leaders%20in%20business%20structure%20their%20workday.%20Reach%20out%20to%20editor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Flauryn-haas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELauryn%20Haas%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20share%20your%20daily%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20started%20researching%20the%20space%20and%20sensed%20that%20the%20'better-for-you'%20trend%20was%20coming%20for%20alcohol.%20Once%20I%20had%20that%20idea%2C%20I%20couldn't%20let%20it%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20launched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.minglemocktails.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMingle%20Mocktails%3C%2Fa%3E%20two%20years%20later%2C%20and%20haven't%20looked%20back.%20Here's%20what%20a%20day%20in%20my%20life%20is%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22baf33f86-ef49-4f2c-96fe-20c32db5e4c3%5C%22%3E2%20a.m.%20%E2%80%94%20reading%20and%20shopping%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20often%20wake%20up%20around%202%20or%203%20a.m.%20I%20read%20on%20my%20Kindle%20for%20a%20bit%20and%20occasionally%20buy%20something%20on%20Amazon%20I%20probably%20don't%20need%20%E2%80%94%20recently%2C%20a%20pencil%20holder%20because%20I%20decided%20my%20desk%20needed%20an%20update.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I'll%20finally%20go%20back%20to%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b32d441a-77b6-445c-a6a2-d73db33c295d%5C%22%3E6%3A30%20a.m.%20%E2%80%94%20attend%20to%20the%20dogs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223465%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20woman%20holds%20two%20dogs%20in%20her%20kitchen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0c744ff246b392afc7b65b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224620%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaylor%20and%20her%20dogs.%3Cp%3EMingle%20Mocktails%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20been%20a%20morning%20person.%20When%20I%20get%20up%2C%20the%20dogs%20come%20first.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20been%20married%20for%20almost%2030%20years.%20Our%20kids%20are%20grown%2C%20so%20our%20two%20dogs%20get%20my%20full%20attention%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20let%20them%20out%2C%20make%20some%20tea%20(my%20go-tos%20are%20Bigelow%20French%20Vanilla%20Chai%20or%20Lavender%20Chamomile)%2C%20and%20ease%20into%20the%20day%20slowly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20year%2C%20I've%20really%20embraced%20what%20I%20call%20the%20art%20of%20puttering.%20That%20early%20window%20is%20the%20only%20time%20in%20my%20day%20that%20feels%20completely%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20take%2015%20minutes%20to%20sit%20with%20my%20tea%20and%20read%20from%20a%20daily%20prayer%20journal%20or%20meditate%20for%20a%20few%20minutes%20using%20the%20Insight%20Timer%20app.%20I%20don't%20always%20remember%20what%20I%20read%20or%20thought%20about%2C%20but%20the%20ritual%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20walk%20the%20dogs%20for%20about%20half%20an%20hour.%20Getting%20outside%20is%20essential%20for%20my%20mental%20freedom.%20Once%20that's%20done%2C%20I%20shower%2C%20and%20then%20it's%20go%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ccbfe648-7615-4a1e-bb61-075a4cefe4eb%5C%22%3E8%20a.m.%20%E2%80%94%20work%20begins%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20my%20work%20is%20done%20in%20my%20home%20office.%20I've%20learned%20to%20check%20my%20calendar%20the%20night%20before%20so%20I'm%20prepared%20for%20the%20next%20day's%20commitments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20days%20are%20a%20mix%20of%20investor%20updates%2C%20sample%20programs%2C%20warehouse%20calls%2C%20performance%20reviews%2C%20and%20production%20forecasting.%20We've%20grown%20quickly%2C%20and%20we've%20run%20out%20of%20product%20several%20times%20in%20the%20last%20year%2C%20so%20production%20forecasting%20is%20a%20huge%20component%20of%20my%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20that%20goes%20wrong%2C%20it's%20a%20full%20fire%20drill%20%E2%80%94%20of%20affected%20customers%20and%20logistics.%20I've%20learned%20the%20hard%20way%20that%20cutting%20things%20too%20close%20isn't%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed5e0048-ce15-4ba3-8ecf-4e6f2a7338a9%5C%22%3E11%20a.m.%20%E2%80%94%20creative%20tasks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20balance%20what%20I%20call%20the%20%26quot%3Byucky%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20like%20budgeting%20and%20financials%2C%20with%20the%20work%20I%20really%20enjoy%2C%20like%20supply%20chain%20and%20operations.%20I%20like%20order%2C%20spreadsheets%2C%20and%20planning%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20get%20through%20the%20tasks%20I%20resist%2C%20I%20reward%20myself%20with%20creative%20work.%20I%20have%20an%20incredible%20marketing%20team%2C%20and%20that's%20where%20I%20get%20the%20most%20joy%3A%20talking%20about%20new%20product%20lines%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.minglemocktails.com%2Fcollections%2Fshop-all-mood%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elike%20Mingle%20Mood%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20our%20functional%20beverage%20line%2C%20packaging%2C%20merch%2C%20or%20silly%20things%20like%20Valentine's%20Day%20stickers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20it%20may%20not%20move%20the%20needle%2C%20but%20it%20keeps%20me%20energized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22096c4678-7f67-4e28-859f-1e7208aec9bc%5C%22%3E12%3A30%20p.m.%20%E2%80%94%20lunch%20and%20back%20to%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELunch%20doesn't%20always%20happen.%20Some%20days%20I'll%20have%20a%20bowl%20of%20watermelon.%20Most%20days%2C%20I%20forage%20%E2%80%94%20a%20handful%20of%20almonds%2C%20or%20whatever's%20in%20the%20fridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcheck-email-less-for-productivity-2016-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebatch%20emails%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20follow%20a%20rigid%20productivity%20system.%20I%20prefer%20to%20respond%20throughout%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20read%20about%20people%20who%20empty%20their%20inboxes%20every%20night%2C%20and%20I%20admire%20them%20from%20afar.%20For%20me%2C%20work%20and%20life%20are%20blurred%20in%20a%20way%20that%20feels%20healthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223951585a-5ea1-4be6-ae22-f516e82a30f3%5C%22%3E3%20p.m.%20%E2%80%94%20checking%20in%20with%20family%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20runs%20sales%20and%20finance%20alongside%20me%2C%20while%20I%20oversee%20marketing%20and%20operations%2C%20and%20my%20son%20oversees%20operations%20and%20logistics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20with%20them%20has%20taught%20me%20something%20important%3A%20my%20son%20is%20the%20only%20person%20who%20will%20truly%20call%20me%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20too%20harsh%20in%20a%20meeting%2C%20he'll%20tell%20me.%20I%20don't%20always%20like%20hearing%20it%2C%20but%20I%20value%20it%20deeply.%20Having%20someone%20you%20trust%20enough%20to%20tell%20you%20the%20truth%20keeps%20you%20grounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f3d5b112-fb81-41f8-a03b-1d4ed0a47643%5C%22%3E6%3A30%20p.m.%20%E2%80%94%20wrapping%20up%20work%20and%20dinner%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20usually%20wrap%20up%20work%20around%206%3A30%20p.m.%2C%20but%20not%20always.%20Sometimes%20my%20reward%20is%20something%20simple%2C%20like%20going%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftj-maxx-vs-marshalls-holiday-shopping-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ET.J.%20Maxx%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20look%20for%20desk%20accessories.%20Other%20nights%2C%20I'll%20work%20a%20little%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nature%20of%20our%20different%20roles%20in%20the%20company%20has%20made%20my%20husband%20the%20cook%20in%20our%20household%2C%20which%20works%20perfectly%2C%20because%20I%20consider%20cooking%20a%20waste%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20happy%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-trader-joes-frozen-lunches-to-buy-dietitian-recommendations-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efrozen%20dinner%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20it%20means%20I%20can%20get%20back%20to%20work.%20He%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20loves%20grilling%2C%20and%20I'm%20very%20supportive%20of%20that%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22681211b8-ef5e-493a-bf72-d69fdb7da5dd%5C%22%3E7%3A30%20p.m.%20%E2%80%94%20winding%20down%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there's%20one%20thing%20I%20protect%20fiercely%2C%20it's%20rest.%20I%20prioritize%20walks%2C%20naps%2C%20and%20downtime%20over%20social%20commitments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20go%20out%20one%20night%20on%20the%20weekend%20and%20keep%20the%20other%20night%20quiet.%20Sunday%20evenings%20are%20for%20puttering%20again%20%E2%80%94%20resetting%20the%20house%20and%20my%20mind%20before%20the%20week%20starts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20dinner%2C%20I%20almost%20always%20have%20a%20lime%20Popsicle.%20They're%20non-negotiable.%20To%20wind%20down%2C%20I%20watch%20shows%20like%20Below%20Deck.%20It's%20pure%20fluff%2C%20and%20that's%20exactly%20what%20I%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220d24a8b7-374b-4ef0-af46-89a803cd1dec%5C%22%3E10%3A45%20p.m.%20%E2%80%94%20Bedtime%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20read%20every%20night%20before%20bed%20%E2%80%94%20always%20fiction%2C%20always%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-kindle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eon%20my%20Kindle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20go%20through%20books%20quickly%2C%20sometimes%20two%20a%20week.%20Romance%2C%20murder%20mysteries%2C%20relationship%20dramas%2C%20whatever%20keeps%20me%20turning%20the%20pages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20always%20on%20my%20phone%2C%20but%20I've%20made%20peace%20with%20that.%20If%20something%20isn't%20urgent%2C%20I%20won't%20respond%20immediately.%20I%20take%20the%20information%20in%20and%20move%20