3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20China's%20Vice%20President%20Han%20Zheng%20as%20Tesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20Nvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Wong%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20could%20provide%20updates%20on%20where%20the%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-stock-nvda-ceo-jensen-huang-short-seller-china-ai-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebusiness%20in%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20stands%20and%20the%20impacts%20the%20chipmaker%20expects%20from%20the%20ongoing%20US%20and%20China%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22210fa736-629d-4769-945e-39c3bf52edc1%5C%22%3EWall%20Street's%20earnings%20expectations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20expect%20Nvidia's%20first%20quarter%20revenue%20to%20come%20in%20at%20%2479.15%20billion%2C%20up%20from%20the%20%2444.1%20billion%20reported%20the%20year%20prior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20center%20revenue%2C%20which%20drives%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20company's%20revenue%2C%20is%20projected%20to%20be%20%2473.49%20billion%2C%20compared%20to%20%2439.1%20billion%20recorded%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsensus%20earnings%20estimates%20are%20at%20%241.78%2C%20up%20from%20the%20%240.81%20recorded%20in%20the%20year-ago%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsensus%20estimates%20signal%20Wall%20Street%20expects%20Nvidia's%20revenue%20outlook%20for%20the%20current%20quarter%20to%20be%20%2487.2%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20stock%20has%20gained%20over%2015%25%20since%20the%20start%20of%202026%2C%20bouncing%20back%20stronger%20on%20reignited%20AI%20enthusiasm.%20Shares%20closed%20at%20%24220.61%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20up%20about%2017%25%20year%20to%20date.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FjrLHZ%2F2%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22468%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20some%20of%20Wall%20Street's%20top%20analysts%20are%20watching%20in%20Nvidia's%20earnings%20print.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223c13c86f-5dcf-49f6-bb69-b1d1268f844c%5C%22%3EThe%20bar%20is%20high%20for%20earnings-driven%20stock%20gains%2C%20Goldman%20says%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EExpectations%20are%20high%20for%20Nvidia%20heading%20into%20the%20earnings%20print.%20The%20AI%20chipmaker%20has%20consistently%20delivered%20beat%20and%20raise%20results%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20fueling%20investor%20expectations%20and%20making%20it%20all%20the%20more%20difficult%20for%20the%20release%20to%20send%20the%20stock%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20analysts%20said%20that%20it's%20not%20a%20question%20of%20if%20the%20chipmaker's%20sales%2C%20earnings%2C%20and%20guidance%20beats%2C%20but%20the%20magnitude%20of%20the%20upside%20relative%20to%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20a%20beat-and-raise%20quarter%20given%20positive%20industry%20supply%20and%20demand%20datapoints%20but%20believe%20the%20bar%20for%20stock%20outperformance%20is%20relatively%20high%20heading%20into%20the%20print%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20the%20stock%20has%20lagged%20peers%20and%20now%20trades%20at%20a%20meaningful%20discount%20relative%20to%20history%2C%20we%20believe%20the%20stock's%20multiple%20can%20re-rate%20if%20we%20see%20evidence%20of%3A%20(1)%20improving%20profitability%20metrics%20at%20hyperscalers%20that%20supports%20sustained%20spending%20growth%3B%20(2)%20proliferation%20of%20agentic%20AI%20signaling%20broader%20enterprise%20adoption%3B%20(3)%20more%20visibility%20into%20deployments%20at%20non-traditional%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20outlined.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20reiterated%20its%20buy%20rating%20and%20%24250%20price%20target%20for%20Nvidia%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fa58c8a7-2321-4ba4-9311-f7cb133d471d%5C%22%3ECiti's%20thoughts%20on%20the%20AI%20chip%20competition%20checkup%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20leads%20the%20AI%20chip%20game%20and%20is%20a%20huge%20beneficiary%20of%20Big%20Tech's%20massive%20AI%20spending%2C%20but%20competition%20within%20the%20AI%20chip%20landscape%20is%20evolving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20Tech%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-new-ai-chips-tpu-inference-training-nvidia-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAlphabet%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-nvidia-aws-ai-chip-dominance-gpu-trainium-inferentia-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20making%20their%20own%20AI%20chips.%20While%20these%20custom%20chips%20and%20other%20CPU%20options%20aren't%20as%20advanced%20as%20Nvidia's%20GPUs%20they%20offer%20an%20alternative%20as%20AI%20moves%20from%20the%20training%20to%20inference%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20changing%20chip%20space%2C%20Citi%20analysts%20indicated%20they%20expect%20GPUs%20to%20represent%20most%20AI%20accelerators%20through%202028.%20Nvidia%2C%20along%20with%20AMD%2C%20are%20driving%20that%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20nevertheless%20still%20expect%20NVDA%20will%20continue%20to%20capture%20the%20bulk%20of%20AI%20accelerators%20investment%20due%20to%20its%20technology%20leadership%20and%20large%20installed%20base%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECiti%20maintained%20a%20buy%20rating%20on%20the%20stock%20and%20a%20%24300%20price%20objective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221bb222a7-ca6c-42a7-b300-7fb7667610d2%5C%22%3EBofA%20says%20boosting%20cash%20returns%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bkey%26quot%3B%20catalyst%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%20said%20that%20Nvidia%20stock%20is%20trading%20at%20a%20compelling%20valuation%2C%20but%20that%20the%20company%20boosting%20cash%20returns%20could%20be%20the%20key%20catalyst%20to%20further%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20chipmaker%20were%20to%20boost%20its%20cash%20returns%20to%20shareholders%20it%20could%20appeal%20to%20dividend%20and%20income-focused%20investors%20and%20ignite%20further%20upside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBofA%20pointed%20out%20that%20Nvidia%20allocated%20less%20than%20half%20of%20its%20free%20cash%20flow%20to%20dividends%20and%20buybacks%20from%202022%20to%202025%2C%20compared%20to%20peers%20that%20returned%20around%2080%25%20in%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoosting%20shareholder%20returns%20could%20expand%20ownership%2C%20close%20NVDA's%20valuation%20gap%20and%20minimize%20circularity%20concerns%20(2H%20catalyst)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20free%20cash%20has%20been%20dedicated%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-100-billion-openai-data-centers-scale-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvesting%20in%20the%20AI%20ecosystem%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20raising%20some%20worries%20about%20circular%20financing%2C%20concerns%20that%20BofA%20noted%20are%20unfair%20in%20their%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chipmaker%20isn't%20the%20only%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-spending-capex-big-tech-stocks-share-buybacks-market-investing-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprioritizing%20AI%20investing%20over%20returning%20cash%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20Goldman%20raising%20this%20concern%20for%20the%20broader%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%20has%20a%20%24320%20price%20target%20and%20a%20buy%20rating%20on%20Nvidia%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2209939ba5-3bc9-48b9-9dcf-eefa95e0e579%5C%22%3EWells%20Fargo%20and%20BofA%20dismiss%20margin%20worries%20on%20input%20cost%20spikes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EConcerns%20about%20the%20sustainability%20of%20Nvidia's%20margins%20have%20emerged%20as%20the%20insatiable%20demand%20for%20compute%20in%20the%20training%20phase%20shifts%20to%20inference.%20These%20worries%20also%20come%20as%20input%20costs%20have%20surged%20recently.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWells%20Fargo%20analysts%20explained%20they're%20not%20viewing%20this%20as%20a%20headwind%20or%20a%20threat%20to%20Nvidia's%20high%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20NVIDIA's%20ability%20to%20largely%20pass%20through%20incremental%20component%20costs%2C%20we%20believe%20the%20company%20can%20maintain%20a%2074%25-75%25%20gross%20margin%20guide%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWells%20Fargo%20recently%20lifted%20its%20price%20target%20to%20%24315%20and%20maintained%20a%20buy%20rating%20for%20Nvidia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Bank%20of%20America%20defended%20Nvidia's%20ability%20to%20maintain%20its%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20as%20Rubin%20Ultra%20(with%20new%20'Kyber'%20rack%20architecture)%20comes%20along%20in%202H27%20and%20as%20HBM%20continues%20to%20represent%20a%20bigger%20part%20of%20build%20cost%2C%20we%20flag%20consensus%20still%20models%20NVDA%20GM%20at%20around%20~74%25%20over%20time%2C%20versus%20current%20~75%25%20range%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-earnings-nvda-stock-price-ai-chips-jensen-huang-china-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779267602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0c86fabe2e5e1daf890889%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-earnings-nvda-stock-price-ai-chips-jensen-huang-china-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nvidia%20stock%20is%20up%2017%25%20in%202026%2C%20but%20has%20pulled%20back%20from%20records.%20Here%20is%20what's%20in%20focus%20for%20investors%20as%20they%20head%20toward%20the%205%20p.m.%20ET%20earnings%20call.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nbuchanan%40insider.com%20(Naomi%20Buchanan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20asked%20top%20startup%20investors%20how%20they%20use%20AI.%20Here's%20what%20they%20said.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jeff%20Fluhr%2C%20Ann%20Miura-Ko%2C%20and%20Sarah%20Smith%20photo%20collage%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0b83af94eb4c909fb2dacb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJeff%20Fluhr%2C%20Ann%20Miura%20Ko%2C%20and%20Sarah%20Smith.%3Cp%3EJeff%20Fluhr%2FCraftVentures%3B%20Ann%20Miura-Ko%2FFloodgate%3B%20Sarah%20Smith%2FSarah%20Smith%20Fund%3B%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EVCs%20are%20increasingly%20using%20AI%20for%20market%20research%20and%20investment%20analysis%20in%20startups.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFloodgate's%20Ann%20Miura%20Ko%20uses%20AI%20to%20analyze%20field%20notes%20and%20identify%20patterns%20in%20AI%20startups.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECraft%20Ventures'%20Jeff%20Fluhr%20uses%20AI%20to%20prototype%20startup%20ideas%20and%20assess%20their%20viability.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EVenture%20capitalists%20have%20spent%20the%20last%20few%20years%20hunting%20for%20the%20next%20great%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-google-executive-wants-to-get-people-off-their-screens-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Increasingly%2C%20they're%20also%20using%20AI%20to%20scout%20for%20the%20next%20OpenAI%20or%20Anthropic.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly-stage%20investors%20are%20weaving%20chatbots%20and%20agents%20into%20nearly%20every%20part%20of%20the%20job%3A%20mapping%20markets%2C%20stress-testing%20ideas%2C%20preparing%20for%20board%20meetings%2C%20and%20turning%20call%20transcripts%20into%20searchable%20knowledge%20bases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20asked%20investors%20from%20this%20year's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseed-100-best-early-stage-vc-investors-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESeed%20100%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseed-40-best-women-early-stage-vc-investors-2026-5%2340.-janet-bannister%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESeed%2040%3C%2Fa%3E%20lists%20about%20how%20they%20use%20AI%20in%20their%20day-to-day%20work%20and%20which%20tools%20they%20rely%20on%20most.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20lightly%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220ccb5e0a-8c2a-4c59-b43e-84d3343c178b%5C%22%3EFor%20building%20a%20second%20brain%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Salil%20Deshpande%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a06c66decd7cc1332baff54%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESalil%20Deshpande%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Salil%20Deshpande%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESalil%20Deshpande%2C%20general%20partner%20at%20Uncorrelated%20Ventures%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BI%20taught%20my%20AI%20agent%20to%20run%20my%20entire%20back%20office.%20It%20handles%20scheduling%20end-to-end%2C%20runs%20email%20campaigns%2C%20and%20triages%20my%20incoming%20LinkedIn%20invitations%2C%20auto-accepting%20portfolio%20founders%20and%20relevant%20VCs%20while%20surfacing%20others%20for%20review.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BIt%20acts%20as%20a%20'portfolio%20doctor.'%20Anyone%20on%20my%20team%20and%20my%20investors%20can%20email%20with%20'portfolio%20doctor'%20in%20the%20subject%20line%20to%20ask%20a%20question%20like%2C%20'What's%20the%20ARR%20or%20Cast.ai%3F'%20It%20will%20dig%20through%20the%20board%20decks%20and%20investor%20updates%20in%20my%20Dropbox%2C%20synthesize%20an%20answer%20with%20specific%20citations%2C%20and%20reply%20to%20the%20email%20thread.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnn%20Miura%20Ko%2C%20partner%20at%20Floodgate%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20I%20spent%20the%20last%20few%20months%20visiting%20a%20dozen%20AI-native%20companies%20in%20person%20to%20document%20how%20they%20actually%20operate%2C%20from%204-person%20startups%20to%20Ramp.%20I%20use%20AI%20to%20ingest%20all%20of%20these%20field%20notes%2C%20cross-reference%20them%20across%20companies%2C%20and%20surface%20patterns%20I'd%20never%20see%20from%20any%20single%20visit.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20become%20the%20empirical%20backbone%20of%20my%20analysis%20of%20the%20AI-pilled%20startup.%20The%20patterns%20are%20converging%20in%20ways%20that%20are%20reshaping%20how%20I%20evaluate%20investments%20and%20founders.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ad54eddf-4f6c-445c-921a-a9dd12ae6bf2%5C%22%3EFor%20finding%20new%20investments%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anne%20Dwane%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a074a7cabc4e9d88574a7bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnne%20Dwane%3Cp%3EChris%20Michel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnne%20Dwane%2C%20cofounder%20and%20general%20partner%20at%20Village%20Global%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BAgentic%20workflows%20help%20us%20pinpoint%20the%20'first-call'%20angels%20in%20today's%20most%20promising%20founder%20ecosystems.%20Networks%20don't%20stay%20fresh%20on%20their%20own%3B%20AI%20helps%20us%20continuously%20extend%20ours%20into%20emerging%20talent%20pools.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlex%20Bard%2C%20managing%20director%20at%20Redpoint%20Ventures%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BWe%20use%20internal%20AI%20systems%20to%20identify%20high-potential%20founders%20leaving%20top%20companies%20and%20detect%20early%20momentum%20signals%20in%20inception-stage%20startups%20(e.g.%2C%20hiring%20velocity%2C%20product%20launches%2C%20network%20activity)%2C%20giving%20us%20a%20sharper%20edge%20in%20sourcing%20before%20companies%20are%20widely%20visible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESarah%20Smith%2C%20general%20partner%20at%20Sarah%20Smith%20Fund%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BI've%20built%20a%20custom%20100-point%20AI%20scoring%20framework%20to%20evaluate%20every%20inbound%20opportunity%20and%20decide%20whether%20to%20take%20a%20first%20meeting.%20It%20systematizes%20my%20thesis%20around%20backing%20'irrationally%20intense'%20founders%20with%20particular%20weight%20on%20the%20Stanford%20ecosystem%2C%20founder-market%20fit%2C%20and%20early%20signs%20of%20exceptional%20achievement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226b17362e-b584-4f9b-9170-38336f1c0707%5C%22%3EFor%20coding%20internal%20tools%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lan%20Xuezhao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a074d34abc4e9d88574a7f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELan%20Xuezhao%3Cp%3EBasis%20Set%20Ventures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELan%20Xuezhao%2C%20founder%20and%20managing%20partner%20at%20Basis%20Set%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20my%20team%20are%20engineers%2C%20and%20we%20have%20been%20launching%20and%20building%20weekly%20with%20AI%20since%202017.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJanet%20Bannister%2C%20founder%20and%20managing%20partner%20at%20Staircase%20Ventures%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BI%20use%20AI%20to%20automatically%20generate%20a%20daily%20schedule%20briefing%20which%20includes%20for%20each%20meeting%3A%20the%20objective%2C%20attendees%20(including%20LinkedIn%20profiles%20of%20people%20I%20do%20not%20know)%2C%20background%20context%20based%20on%20previous%20emails%20and%20meetings%2C%20and%20links%20to%20appropriate%20documents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJeff%20Fluhr%2C%20venture%20partner%20at%20Craft%20Ventures%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BI%20use%20AI%20every%20day%20to%20turn%20venture%20ideas%20into%20real%20products.%20Beyond%20researching%20companies%20and%20technologies%2C%20I%20use%20AI%20coding%20tools%20to%20prototype%20my%20own%20startup%20ideas%20so%20I%20can%20evaluate%20them%20more%20fully%20and%20decide%20whether%20to%20bring%20them%20to%20life.%20In%20the%20last%20four%20months%2C%20I've%20built%20four%20such%20products.%20That%20has%20changed%20how%20I%20evaluate%20new%20ideas%3A%20instead%20of%20debating%20them%20in%20the%20abstract%2C%20I%20can%20get%20to%20a%20working%20prototype%20quickly%20and%20see%20what%20actually%20holds%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShan-Lyn%20Ma%2C%20cofounder%20and%20co-CEO%20of%20Zola%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20pushing%20myself%20to%20adopt%20an%20AI-first%20mindset%20across%20everything%20I%20do%2C%20both%20at%20work%20and%20in%20my%20personal%20life.%20I%20built%20a%20custom%20'Gem'%20in%20Gemini%20that%20tracks%20any%20new%20fundraising%20or%20exit%20news%20from%20any%20day%20of%20the%20roughly%2050%20portfolio%20companies%20I've%20invested%20in%20to%20provide%20me%20with%20a%20daily%20summary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e598eb6f-c0ea-4cf9-910d-b90c5a3d7f92%5C%22%3EFor%20prepping%20for%20pitches%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Henry%20McNamara%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a06cab8abc4e9d88574a4ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHenry%20McNamara%3Cp%3EGreat%20Oaks%20Venture%20Capital%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHenry%20McNamara%2C%20partner%20at%20Great%20Oaks%20Venture%20Capital%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20able%20to%20use%20natural%20language%20to%20ask%20very%20specific%20questions%20and%20get%20hard%20data%20back%20helps%20prepare%20for%20every%20pitch%20I%20take.%20Given%20we%20are%20a%20generalist%20firm%20taking%20pitches%20in%20many%20different%20industries%2C%20I%20am%20definitely%20more%20informed%20and%20prepared%20for%20pitches%20than%20I%20was%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20using%20Claude%20to%20steelman%20my%20reasoning%20and%20logic%20for%20investing%20or%20passing.%20It%20helps%20bring%20in%20all%20types%20of%20different%20data%20to%20test%20ideas%2C%20biases%2C%20and%20blind%20spots%20before%20we%20debate%20them%20internally%20as%20a%20team.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESara%20Deshpande%2C%20general%20partner%20at%20Maven%20Ventures%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BPerplexity%20is%20my%20new%20teammate.%20I%20use%20it%20for%20everything%3A%20market%20research%2C%20market%20sizing%2C%20competitive%20research%2C%20target%20investor%20lists%2C%20learning%20more%20about%20founders%2C%20prepping%20pre-reads%20before%20meeting%20a%20new%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJon%20Soberg%2C%20CEO%20and%20managing%20partner%20at%20MS%26amp%3BAD%20Ventures%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20see%20a%20company%20that%20I%20really%20like%2C%20I'm%20able%20to%20scan%20the%20market%20quickly%20to%20get%20a%20feel%20for%20the%20competitive%20landscape%2C%20which%20is%20more%20important%20than%20ever%20in%20our%20increasingly%20AI-native%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c2dc220-1be1-4aba-b8a1-0efac3c394b8%5C%22%3EFor%20spending%20more%20time%20IRL%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJulie%20Lein%2C%20managing%20partner%20at%20Urban%20Innovation%20Fund%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BMore%20than%20anything%2C%20AI%20made%20our%20team%20deeply%20aware%20of%20the%20importance%20of%20humanity%20in%20the%20tech%20and%20startup%20world.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we've%20been%20leaning%20even%20more%20aggressively%20toward%20in-person%20events%2C%20founder%20meetings%2C%20coffee%20chats%2C%20and%20beyond.%20Because%2C%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI%2C%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20stands%20out%20is%20real%20human-to-human%20interaction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-venture-capital-investors-use-ai-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779267601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0b83af94eb4c909fb2dacb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-venture-capital-investors-use-ai-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Venture%20capitalists%2C%20including%20Ann%20Miura-Ko%20and%20Salil%20Deshpande%2C%20are%20leveraging%20AI%20for%20investment%20insights%2C%20deal%20sourcing%2C%20and%20developing%20internal%20tools.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mrussell%40businessinsider.com%20(Melia%20Russell%2CLeena%20Rao%2CBen%20Bergman%2CSydney%20Bradley%2CTom%20Carter%2CRosalie%20Chan%2CShubhangi%20Goel%2CRobert%20Scammell%2CGeoff%20Weiss%2CCharles%20Rollet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chopper%20Carrying%20Delhi%20Family%20Hits%20Power%20Line%2C%20Lands%20In%20Field%20In%20Uttarakhand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22According%20to%20reports%2C%20a%20technical%20issue%20developed%20in%20the%20Trans%20Bharat%20Aviation%20company's%20helicopter%20while%20it%20was%20flying%20over%20the%20Chamba-Arakot%20area%20around%208.30%20am.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779267397000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F20