n%20a%20scooter%20she%20had%20stolen%20from%20her%20father.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779266675000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2026-05%2Fo479lckg_maharashtra-woman-abandons-children-elopes-with-lover-_625x300_20_May_26.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoman-elopes-with-lover-leaves-children-on-a-bus-they-dont-have-parents-11521952%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20woman%20seated%20her%20two%20children%20on%20the%20Pandharpur-Sambhaji%20Nagar%20bus%20and%20departed%20with%20her%20lover%20on%20a%20scooter%20she%20had%20stolen%20from%20her%20father.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Your%20entry-level%20job%20is%20getting%20harder%20thanks%20to%20AI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224724%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20career%20fair%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0d137ebe2e5e1daf890c2d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222362%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20entry-level%20job%20isn't%20disappearing%2C%20but%20expectations%20may%20change%20because%20of%20AI%2C%20according%20to%20a%20survey.%3Cp%3EJean-Fran%C3%A7ois%20Fort%2FHans%20Lucas%20via%20Reuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20has%20stoked%20fears%20that%20entry-level%20jobs%20are%20disappearing%20as%20it%20automates%20some%20skills.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20survey%20showed%20that%20employers%20still%20see%20an%20increase%20in%20demand%20in%20certain%20entry-level%20roles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20bar%20for%20the%20type%20of%20work%20entry-level%20workers%20will%20be%20doing%20is%20increasing%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-new-grads-can-stand-out-in-slow-job-market-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eentry-level%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20not%20disappear%20en%20masse%20due%20to%20AI%2C%20but%20it%20could%20make%20the%20role%20harder%2C%20a%20new%20survey%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20report%20published%20Tuesday%20that%20surveyed%201%2C500%20executives%20showed%20that%20while%20nearly%20half%20of%20respondents%20expect%20AI%20to%20have%20a%20positive%20impact%20on%20demand%20for%20entry-level%20employees%2C%20they%20also%20see%20AI%20emphasizing%20different%20skill%20sets%20for%20those%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20by%20the%20Strada%20Institute%20for%20the%20Future%20of%20Work%2C%20found%20that%2042%25%20of%20employers%20who%20explored%20using%20AI%20saw%20that%20the%20technology%20%26quot%3Bincreased%20analytical%20and%20judgement-based%20responsibilities%26quot%3B%20while%2041%25%20say%20it%20%26quot%3Breduced%20routine%20or%20administrative%20tasks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20tech%2C%2060%25%20of%20employers%20who%20explored%20using%20AI%20saw%20an%20increase%20in%20analytical%20and%20judgment-based%20responsibilities%20for%20entry-level%20workers%2C%20and%2054%25%20saw%20a%20reduced%20need%20for%20jobs%20that%20cover%20routine%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEmployers%20expecting%20AI%20to%20increase%20entry-level%20hiring%20report%20these%20roles%20are%20becoming%20more%20complex%2C%20while%20those%20expecting%20to%20hire%20fewer%20people%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20automate%20basic%20tasks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sentiment%20is%20not%20evenly%20seen%20across%20industries.%20Within%20hospitality%2C%20leisure%2C%20and%20arts%2C%2028%25%20saw%20an%20increase%20in%20analytical%20and%20judgment-based%20skills%20and%20a%2035%25%20reduction%20in%20routine%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Cuban%2C%20billionaire%20and%20founder%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it's%20hard%20to%20draw%20conclusions%20from%20the%20report%20alone.%20Still%2C%20he%20said%20it%20makes%20sense%20that%20companies%20are%20now%20expecting%20more%20out%20of%20junior%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20people%20thought%20of%20as%20an%20entry-level%20position%20before%20%E2%80%94%20show%20up%20and%20do%20the%20tedious%20work%20%E2%80%94%20is%20gone%2C%26quot%3B%20Cuban%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20when%20companies%20hire%20they%20expect%20you%20to%20hit%20the%20ground%20running.%20No%20matter%20your%20background%2C%26quot%3B%20Cuban%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhich%20makes%20sense%20because%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20compete%20in%20a%20new%20AI%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI's%20advancement%20has%20sparked%20concerns%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftheres-more-bad-news-for-entry-level-coders-ai-study-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eentry-level%20role%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20getting%20harder%20to%20come%20by%2C%20especially%20for%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-ladder-software-engineers-collapsing-ai-google-meta-coding-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esoftware%20engineers%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20Big%20Tech%20continues%20to%20trim%20head%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20one%20study%20published%20last%20year%20showed%2067%25%20of%20public-company%20CEOs%20surveyed%20said%20they%20expect%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-hiring-comeback-entry-level-jobs-ceo-teneo-survey-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20to%20increase%20entry-level%20hiring%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Strada%20report%20similarly%20found%20that%20executives%20who%20expect%20to%20increase%20hiring%20due%20to%20AI%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20have%20strategically%20integrated%20AI%20tools%2C%20meaning%20%26quot%3Bthey%20have%20a%20clear%2C%20company-wide%20plan%20for%20using%20AI%20across%20all%20their%20teams%20to%20help%20the%20business%20succeed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fentry-level-jobs-more-skilled-impact-from-ai-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779266461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0d1362ce0a5b2f12d7d9d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fentry-level-jobs-more-skilled-impact-from-ai-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20survey%20of%201%2C500%20employees%20showed%20AI%20isn't%20destroying%20entry-level%20jobs%20but%20the%20type%20of%20work%20expected%20is%20changing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Economic%20storm%20brewing%20%26amp%3Bamp%3B%20...'%3A%20Rahul%20takes%20'nautanki'%20swipe%20at%20PM%20's%20gift%20to%20Meloni%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779266451000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131221716%2Cimgsize-52682.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Feconomic-storm-brewing-and-rahul-gandhi-takes-nautanki-swipe-at-pm-modis-melody-gift-to-meloni%2Farticleshow%2F131221712.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi%20criticized%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20gifting%20toffees%20to%20Italian%20counterpart%20Giorgia%20Meloni%20in%20Rome%2C%20while%20accusing%20him%20of%20%26quot%3Blaughing%20and%20filming%20reels%26quot%3B%20amid%20the%20struggles%20of%20farmers%2C%20youth%2C%20women%2C%20workers%2C%20and%20small%20traders%20in%20India.%20Gandhi%20deemed%20the%20gesture%20%26quot%3Ba%20farce%26quot%3B%20and%20not%20leadership%2C%20contrasting%20it%20with%20an%20%26quot%3Beconomic%20storm%26quot%3B%20brewing%20domestically.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Billy%20Joel%20condemns%20upcoming%20biopi