h%20platform%20that%20happens%20to%20serve%20pomegranate-glazed%20salmon%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcava-review-photos-salad-bowl-chain-expansion-chicago-food-restaurant-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eharissa%20chicken%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20Brett%20Schulman%20said%20the%20company%20was%20laying%20the%20groundwork%20to%20become%20%26quot%3Ba%20real-time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyour-favorite-restaurant-is-becoming-a-tech-company-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-enabled%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20as%20Cava%20builds%20out%20its%20internal%20data%20and%20commerce%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%20has%20unveiled%20two%20new%20systems%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BCava%20Core%2C%26quot%3B%20its%20centralized%20data%20platform%2C%20and%20%26quot%3BCava%20Current%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20real-time%20operating%20platform%20now%20processing%20orders%20across%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20Schulman%20said%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20systems%20will%20allow%20Cava%20to%20create%20%26quot%3Bmore%20meaningful%2C%20personalized%20experiences%26quot%3B%20for%20guests%20while%20helping%20stores%20%26quot%3Banticipate%20demand%20and%20better%20align%20staffing%20and%20preparation%20in%20real%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20practice%2C%20that%20means%20AI-powered%20forecasting%2C%20predictive%20labor%20scheduling%2C%20inventory%20management%2C%20and%20personalized%20digital%20marketing%20%E2%80%94%20all%20aimed%20at%20making%20the%20healthy-bowl%20chain%20faster%2C%20more%20efficient%2C%20and%20more%20addictive%2C%20so%20guests%20keep%20coming%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERestaurant%20chains%20are%20aggressively%20leaning%20into%20AI%20as%20the%20fast-casual%20category%20becomes%20more%20crowded%20and%20consumers%20grow%20more%20selective%20about%20where%20they%20spend%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECava%20reported%209.7%25%20same-restaurant%20sales%20growth%20and%206.8%25%20traffic%20growth%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%2C%20with%20executives%20saying%20the%20company's%20lower-income%20customer%20cohorts%20are%20outperforming%20other%20income%20brackets%20as%20broader%20restaurant%20traffic%20softens.%20Executives%20also%20repeatedly%20stressed%20that%20Cava%20has%20avoided%20aggressive%20discounting%2C%20opting%20instead%20to%20position%20itself%20as%20a%20value%20play%20with%20premium%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETechnology%20%E2%80%94%20not%20hummus%20%E2%80%94%20increasingly%20appears%20to%20be%20central%20to%20the%20company's%20growth%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Grain%20bowls%20from%20the%20Mediterranean%20chain%20Cava.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0cf34a7684ba33f7380894%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECava's%20AI%20systems%2C%20Cava%20Core%20and%20Cava%20Current%2C%20aim%20to%20personalize%20customer%20experiences%20and%20optimize%20restaurant%20operations.%3Cp%3EDixie%20D.%20Vereen%2FFor%20The%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESchulman%20described%20the%20effort%20as%20Cava%20%26quot%3Bbeing%20on%20the%20precipice%20of%20a%20decade%20of%20data%20transformation%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%20the%20goal%20over%20the%20coming%20years%20is%20to%20create%20a%20connected%20system%20that%20brings%20%26quot%3Bdata%2C%20applications%2C%20and%20intelligence%20together%20to%20power%20our%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImportantly%2C%20he%20said%20the%20technology%20was%20meant%20to%20%26quot%3Benhance%20the%20human%20experience%2C%20not%20replace%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20from%20Cava's%20earnings%20call%20was%20clear%3A%20the%20chain%20is%20entering%20its%20AI%20era%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20the%20Mediterranean%20restaurant%20isn't%20the%20only%20slop%20bowl%20provider%20to%20bet%20big%20on%20technology%20as%20fast-casual%20chai