%20like%20Kalshi%20and%20Polymarket.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20a%20government%20agency%20is%20fighting%20the%20ban%2C%20suing%20Gov.%20Tim%20Walz%20for%20signing%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPrediction%20markets%20have%20faced%20backlash%20from%20lawmakers%20who%20say%20they%20enable%20insider%20trading%20and%20gambling.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMinnesota%20has%20become%20the%20first%20state%20to%20ban%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprediction-market-event-analysis-outlook-polymarket-insider-trading-market-manipulation-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprediction%20markets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20fight%20over%20these%20platforms'%20right%20to%20operate%20is%20far%20from%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Minnesota%20Gov.%20Tim%20Walz%20signed%20and%20approved%20a%20state%20ban%20on%20prediction%20markets.%20Per%20the%20bill%2C%20any%20person%20who%20creates%2C%20operates%2C%20or%20advertises%20a%20prediction%20market%20that%20involves%20wagers%20on%20events%20such%20as%20sports%2C%20elections%2C%20and%20government%20actions%20will%20be%20guilty%20of%20a%20felony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ban%20is%20set%20to%20go%20into%20effect%20on%20August%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20the%20bill%20was%20passed%2C%20the%20US%20Commodity%20Futures%20Trading%20Commission%2C%20or%20CFTC%2C%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20Minnesota%20and%20Walz%20to%20block%20the%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20it%20regulates%20trades%20in%20prediction%20markets%2C%20such%20as%20Kalshi%20and%20Polymarket%2C%20and%20Minnesota%20cannot%20criminalize%20them%20under%20state%20law.%20It%20added%20in%20a%20Tuesday%20press%20release%20that%20Walz's%20legislation%20will%20%26quot%3Bundermine%20the%20federal%20regulatory%20regime%20set%20up%20by%20Congress%20more%20than%2050%20years%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20Minnesota%20law%20turns%20lawful%20operators%20and%20participants%20in%20prediction%20markets%20into%20felons%20