3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fssnlf-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESamsung%20Electronics%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20become%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20artificial-intelligence%20boom.%20Now%20the%20company%20faces%20a%20battle%20over%20who%20deserves%20a%20share%20of%20the%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETalks%20between%20Samsung%20and%20its%20largest%20labor%20union%20broke%20down%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.yna.co.kr%2Fview%2FAEN20260520005500320%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYonhap%20news%20agency%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20putting%20around%2048%2C000%20workers%20on%20track%20to%20begin%20an%2018-day%20strike%20on%20Thursday%20over%20bonuses%20and%20profit-sharing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamsung%20shares%20tanked%20as%20much%20as%205%25%20after%20reports%20that%20negotiations%20had%20collapsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dispute%20comes%20at%20a%20sensitive%20moment%20for%20Samsung%2C%20which%20recently%20joined%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouth-korea-stock-market-samsung-1-trillion-club-ai-boom-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrillion-dollar%20club%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20investors%20piled%20into%20AI-linked%20semiconductor%20stocks.%20The%20tech%20titan's%20stock%20price%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamsung%20sits%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20AI%20supply%20chain%20through%20its%20memory-chip%20business%2C%20which%20makes%20high-bandwidth%20memory%20chips%20used%20in%20AI%20servers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fallout%20from%20a%20prolonged%20labor%20dispute%20could%20stretch%20far%20beyond%20temporary%20production%20disruptions%2C%20wrote%20Jing%20Jie%20Yu%2C%20an%20equity%20analyst%20at%20Morningstar%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20key%20obstacle%20is%20Samsung's%20refusal%20to%20formalize%20profit-sharing%20in%20contracts%2C%26quot%3B%20Yu%20wrote%20in%20a%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYu%20warned%20that%20Samsung%20risks%20falling%20behind%20rivals%20if%20it%20fails%20to%20offer%20more%20competitive%20compensation.%20He%20pointed%20to%20rival%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-memory-chip-boom-next-trillion-dollar-company-sk-hynix-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESK%20Hynix%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20shares%2010%25%20of%20operating%20profits%20with%20employees%20and%20scrapped%20bonus%20caps%20for%20a%20decade%2C%20arguing%20that%20Samsung's%20weaker%20pay%20structure%20could%20hurt%20the%20company%20both%20immediately%20and%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYu%20estimated%20that%20an%2018-day%20strike%20could%20cut%20Samsung's%202026%20operating%20profit%20by%20about%205%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bigger%20concern%20is%20talent%2C%20as%20weaker%20compensation%20could%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20Samsung%20to%20retain%20and%20attract%20the%20engineers%20needed%20to%20stay%20competitive%20in%20the%20AI%20chip%20race%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everyone%20believes%20the%20labor%20dispute%20will%20derail%20Samsung's%20AI-driven%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeff%20Kim%2C%20the%20head%20of%20technology%20research%20at%20South%20Korea's%20KB%20Securities%2C%20said%20concerns%20around%20strikes%20and%20bonuses%20have%20likely%20already%20been%20priced%20into%20the%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarnings%20momentum%20should%20mount%20further%20regardless%20of%20strike%20concerns%2C%26quot%3B%20Kim%20wrote%20in%20a%20Wednesday%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKim%20argued%20that%20demand%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchip-semiconductor-stock-gains-spread-beyond-nvidia-cpu-memory-sandisk-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20memory%20chips%3C%2Fa%3E%20remains%20stronger%20than%20available%20supply%20as%20major%20US%20tech%20companies%20continue%20pouring%20money%20into%20AI%20infrastructure.%20That%20spending%20boom%2C%20he%20said%2C%20should%20continue%20lifting%20chip%20prices%20and%20profits%20even%20as%20labor%20tensions%20escalate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamsung's%20labor%20dispute%20is%20feeding%20into%20a%20broader%20political%20debate%20over%20who%20should%20share%20in%20the%20gains%20from%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20South%20Korea's%20presidential%20policy%20chief%2C%20Kim%20Yong-beom%2C%20said%20some%20of%20the%20profits%20and%20tax%20revenues%20generated%20by%20AI%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bstructurally%20returned%20to%20all%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20arguing%20the%20gains%20were%20built%20on%20decades%20of%20national%20industrial%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20official's%20Facebook%20post%20on%20Monday%20night%20roiled%20South%20Korea's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-south-korea-kospi-stock-market-outlook-ai-boom-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ered-hot%20stock%20market%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20sending%20the%20benchmark%20Kospi%20index%20down%20by%20as%20much%20as%205.1%25%20the%20next%20day.%20Samsung%20and%20rival%20SK%20Hynix%20shares%20also%20dropped%20sharply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kospi%20has%20surged%20about%2065%25%20this%20year%20after%20hitting%20a%20record%20high%20last%20Thursday%2C%20fueled%20by%20investor%20enthusiasm%20around%20AI-linked%20chipmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20benchmark%20index%20%E2%80%94%20in%20which%20Samsung%20accounts%20for%20roughly%20a%20third%20of%20the%20weighting%20%E2%80%94%20was%20down%20over%202%25%20by%20midday%20Wednesday%20as%20concerns%20over%20the%20labor%20dispute%20rattled%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsamsung-ai-chip-trillion-dollar-boom-profit-sharing-worker-strike-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779256492000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0d25f2ce0a5b2f12d7da0d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsamsung-ai-chip-trillion-dollar-boom-profit-sharing-worker-strike-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Samsung's%20AI-driven%20success%20faces%20a%20challenge%20as%2048%2C000%20employees%20prepare%20to%20strike%20over%20bonus%20disputes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukrainians%20tricked%20out%20their%20long-range%20exploding%20drones%20to%20unleash%20rocket%20fire%20on%20Russian%20air%20defenses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222482%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22White%20rocket%20streaks%20hurtle%20toward%20a%20ground%20target.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0d3b3ebe2e5e1daf890c96%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20troops%20posted%20drone-camera%20footage%20of%20rockets%20appearing%20to%20fly%20from%20the%20wings%20of%20the%20uncrewed%20aircraft%20toward%20a%20Russian%20naval%20base.%3Cp%3EUnmanned%20Systems%20Forces%20and%20Magyar%20Birds%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUkraine%20has%20been%20mounting%20rocket%20pods%20on%20its%20one-way%20attack%20drones%20to%20strike%20Russia's%20rear.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20combo%20lets%20the%20drone%20launch%20up%20to%20eight%20rockets%20while%20reserving%20its%20warhead%20for%20primary%20threats.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20unit%20said%20it%20carried%20out%20the%20attacks%20about%20300%20miles%20deep.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20been%20fitting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-drones-hit-deep-in-russia-security-source-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elong-range%20attack%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20cheap%20unguided%20rockets%2C%20using%20them%20in%20the%20Russian%20rear%20to%20bombard%20strategic%20assets%20and%20suppress%20air%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Unmanned%20Systems%20Forces%2C%20or%20USF%2C%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20units%20had%20equipped%20fixed-wing%20exploding%20d