D%5C%22Mindy%20Kaling.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0d25e2ce0a5b2f12d7da0b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMindy%20Kaling%20says%20having%20kids%20made%20her%20rethink%20her%20health.%3Cp%3EChad%20Salvador%2FWWD%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMindy%20Kaling%20says%20having%20kids%20made%20her%20more%20conscious%20about%20her%20health.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20her%20motivation%20to%20be%20fit%20is%20no%20longer%20vanity%2C%20but%20wanting%20to%20%26quot%3Blive%20at%20least%2020%20more%20years%26quot%3B%20for%20her%20kids.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEven%20so%2C%20Kaling%20said%20she%20understands%20why%20her%20weight%20loss%20can%20spark%20strong%20public%20reactions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmindy-kaling-career-how-she-makes-spends-money-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMindy%20Kaling%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20becoming%20a%20mom%20changed%20the%20way%20she%20thinks%20about%20her%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bustle.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmindy-kaling-interview-not-suitable-for-work-running-point%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20Bustle%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20interview%20published%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Kaling%20reflected%20on%20her%20weight-loss%20journey%20and%20the%20public%20scrutiny%20that%20comes%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20sometimes%20no%20fun%20when%20one%20of%20your%20favorite%20actors%20loses%20weight.%20You%20have%20an%20idea%20of%20what%20they%20were%20like%20when%20you%20grew%20attached%20to%20them%2C%20and%20it%20made%20them%20endear%20themselves%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaling%20said.%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20it's%20never%20a%20joy%20to%20be%20scrutinized%2C%20but%20also%20I%20truly%20understand%20it%2C%20as%20someone%20who%20consumes%20pop%20culture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Kaling%20has%20long%20been%20open%20about%20not%20fitting%20Hollywood's%20traditional%20beauty%20ideals%2C%20she%20said%20her%20fitness%20journey%20is%20now%20driven%20by%20the%20need%20to%20%26quot%3Blive%20at%20least%2020%20more%20years%26quot%3B%20for%20her%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20I%20wake%20up%20every%20day%20being%20like%2C%20'I%20look%20amazing%20and%20I'm%20so%20gorgeous'%3F%20No%2C%20unsurprisingly%2C%20but%20I%20truly%20feel%20so%20healthy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaling%20has%20two%20daughters%20and%20one%20son%2C%20but%20has%20never%20publicly%20revealed%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20children's%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20added%20her%20goals%20around%20weight%20and%20fitness%20look%20very%20different%20now%20than%20they%20did%20earlier%20in%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20younger%2C%20I%20would%20want%20to%20lose%20weight%20because%20of%20vanity%20reasons.%20Now%20I%20want%20to%20lose%20weight%20or%20have%20lost%20weight%20because%20I%20want%20to%20stave%20off%20things%20like%20diabetes.%20I%20had%20it%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20my%20family%2C%20and%20trying%20to%20avoid%20those%20kinds%20of%20things%20will%2C%20I%20think%2C%20help%20longevity%20for%20me%2C%20and%20that's%20my%20goal%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Kaling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fhealth%2Fmindy-kaling-says-it-took-a-long-time-to-let-go-of-losing-weight-for-vanity-reasons%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20People%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20was%20trying%20to%20build%20a%20healthier%20relationship%20with%20exercise%2C%20after%20years%20of%20viewing%20it%20as%20something%20that%20needed%20to%20feel%20punishing%20to%20be%20effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20really%20been%20mixing%20it%20up%20and%20knowing%20that%20if%20a%20workout%20doesn't%20necessarily%20make%20me%20soak%20my%20clothes%20with%20sweat%2C%20that%20it%20still%20was%20a%20good%20workout%E2%80%A6%20It%20does%20not%20have%20to%20be%20punishing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prevention.com%2Fhealth%2Fa60827566%2Fmindy-kaling-diet-fitness-routine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Prevention%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20stays%20active%20through%20strength%20training%20and%20walking%2015%20to%2020%20miles%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20have%20any%20phone%20call%2C%20I%20just%20pick%20up%20the%20phone%20and%20I%20just%20go%20for%20a%20walk.%20Sometimes%20I%20listen%20to%20music%2C%20but%20it's%20been%20such%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20get%20three%20to%20five%20miles%20a%20day%20of%20walking%20and%20movement%2C%20which%20I%20think%20is%20really%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaling%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmindy-kaling-having-kids-weight-loss-journey-fitness-health-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779253321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0d25e2ce0a5b2f12d7da0b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmindy-kaling-having-kids-weight-loss-journey-fitness-health-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDo%20I%20wake%20up%20every%20day%20being%20like%2C%20'I%20look%20amazing%20and%20I'm%20so%20gorgeous'%3F%20No%2C%20unsurprisingly%2C%20but%20I%20truly%20feel%20so%20healthy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mindy%20Kaling%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40businessinsider.com%20(Amanda%20Goh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A97%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jon%20Stewart%20Showers%20Stephen%20Colbert%20With%20Gifts%20in%20Honor%20of%20%E2%80%98The%20Late%20Show%E2%80%99s%E2%80%99%20Final%20Week%3A%20%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20Confuse%20Cancellation%20With%20Failure%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779253007000%2C%22visual%22