se-argument-trading-timing-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanipulating%20the%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20deceiving%20retail%20investors%20with%20a%20plan%20that%20earned%20him%20more%20than%20%2420%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20said%20Left%20was%20working%20with%20hedge%20funds%20and%20sharing%20in%20some%20of%20their%20trading%20profits.%20They've%20accused%20him%20of%20concealing%20those%20relationships%20in%20order%20to%20%26quot%3Bmaintain%20the%20illusion%20of%20Citron's%20independence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEliza%20Goldberg%2C%20a%20chief%20compliance%20officer%20at%20Atom%2C%20a%20Texas-based%20hedge%20fund%2C%20testified%20in%20a%20Los%20Angeles%20federal%20court%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20Left%20was%20paid%20more%20than%20%242.6%20million%20by%20the%20fund%20for%20providing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrew-left-trial-short-seller-doj-securities-fraud-citron-research-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrading%20recommendations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%2C%20who%20say%20Left%20hid%20that%20work%20from%20retail%20investors%2C%20said%20some%20of%20those%20payments%20were%20made%20weeks%20before%20Left%20published%20a%20report%20criticizing%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrew-left-trial-short-seller-doj-securities-fraud-citron-research-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eactivist%20short%20seller%3C%2Fa%3E's%20work%20with%20a%20hedge%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202019%2C%20Harry%20Markopolos%2C%20the%20famous%20whistleblower%20of%20the%20Bernie%20Madoff%20scandal%2C%20issued%20a%20short%20report%20on%20General%20Electric%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20fraud%20%26quot%3Bbigger%20than%20Enron.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeft%20issued%20a%20rebuttal%20tweet%20and%20report%2C%20calling%20Markopolos'%20credibility%20into%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20noted%20in%20the%20disclaimer%20on%20his%20site%2C%20Harry%20is%20being%20paid%20a%20%25%20of%20profits%20from%20an%20unnamed%20hedge%20fund%20that%20is%20short%20GE%2C%26quot%3B%20Left%20wrote%20in%20the%20report.%20%26quot%3BNo%20credible%20hedge%20fund%20or%20short%20seller%20would%20ever%20do%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeft's%20report%20also%20said%20regarding%20his%20own%20activity%2C%20that%20Citron%20had%20never%20been%20paid%20to%20publish%20research%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bcompensation%20tied%20to%20the%20'success%20of%20a%20trade'%20would%20not%20pass%20internal%20compliance%20nor%20would%20it%20pass%20compliance%20of%20any%20fund%20that%20Citron%20would%20collaborate%20with%20on%20ideas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrew-left-defense-goes-on-offense-securities-fraud-trial-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELeft's%20defense%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggested%20his%20claims%20about%20Markopolos'%20work%20with%20a%20hedge%20fund%20were%20not%20a%20one-to-one%20comparison%20with%20Left's.%20They've%20argued%20that%20there%20was%20no%20rule%20or%20law%20preventing%20Left%20from%20working%20with%20a%20hedge%20fund.%20They%20also%20said%20the%20agreements%20with%20Atom%20had%20a%20confidentiality%20clause%20that%20would've%20prevented%20Left%20from%20publicly%20disclosing%20he%20was%20working%20with%20the%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20have%20also%20accused%20Left%20of%20coordinating%20with%20at%20least%20one%20hedge%20fund%2C%20Anson%20Funds%2C%20to%20draft%20Citron%20reports%20and%20tweets%2C%20and%20that%20Anson%20would%20make%20trades%20tied%20to%20those%20reports%2C%20sharing%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20profits%20with%20Left.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EText%20messages%20showed%20in%20court%20included%20exchanges%20between%20Left%20and%20a%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20Anson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3Bthe%20best%20shorts%20are%20retail%20shorts%20no%20doubt%2C%26quot%3B%20Left%20wrote%20in%20a%20text%2C%20referring%20to%20stocks%20that%20are%20owned%20by%20a%20lot%20of%20retail%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3Bwe%20can%20DESTROY%20CRON%2C%26quot%3B%20Left%20said%20in%20another%20text%20message%2C%20which%20prosecutors%20said%20was%20a%20reference%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshort-seller-andrew-left-trial-opening-statements-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECronos%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20cannabis%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20report%20on%20Cronos%20was%20released%2C%20Left%20wrote%20in%20a%20text%20to%20the%20portfolio%20manager%20that%20once%20he%20realized%20who%20owned%20the%20stock%2C%20it%20was%20like%20taking%20%26quot%3Bcandy%20from%20a%20baby.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20said%20Left%20was%20paid%20over%20%241.1%20million%20from%20Anson%20related%20to%20trades%20on%20two%20other%20cannabis%20stocks%2C%20Namaste%20Technologies%20and%20India%20Globalization%20Capital.%20They%20also%20said%20he%20got%20the%20money%20through%20a%20third%20party%20that%20Left%20invoiced%20for%20%26quot%3Bconsulting%20services.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20defense%20said%20Left%20may%20have%20consulted%20industry%20experts%2C%20like%20Anson%2C%20which%20was%20in%20the%20cannabis%20space%2C%20but%20that%20reports%20put%20out%20by%20Citron%20were%20his%20honest%20views.%20They%20said%20Anson%2C%20based%20in%20Canada%2C%20had%20better%20access%20to%20the%20stocks%20Left%20was%20interested%20in%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20said%20Left's%20%26quot%3Bcandy%20from%20a%20baby%26quot%3B%20comment%20referred%20not%20to%20retail%20investors%20broadly%20but%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%26quot%3B%20of%20people%20who%20sent%20him%20vile%20emails%20after%20he%20published%20the%20short%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrew-left-paid-millions-hedge-funds-prosecutors-allege-madoff-whistleblower-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1