ssed%20in%20black.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0a8d6594eb4c909fb2d5c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChatrine%20Siswoyo%20moved%20to%20Hong%20Kong%20for%20her%20husband's%20job%20opportunity.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Chatrine%20Siswoyo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChatrine%20Siswoyo%2C%20now%2040%2C%20has%20built%20a%20career%20across%20companies%20including%20Philips%2C%20Uber%2C%20Netflix%2C%20and%20ByteDance.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETen%20years%20ago%2C%20she%20left%20her%20dream%20job%20at%20Twitter%20to%20relocate%20to%20Hong%20Kong%20for%20her%20husband's%20role.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStarting%20anew%20without%20a%20job%20forced%20her%20to%20confront%20who%20she%20was%20beyond%20her%20career.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Chatrine%20Siswoyo%2C%20a%20communications%20leader.%20Her%20words%20have%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20turned%2040%20this%20year%2C%20and%20I%20still%20think%20about%20the%20moment%20I%20almost%20forgot%20how%20to%20define%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20happened%2010%20years%20ago%20on%20a%20plane.%20We%20were%20flying%20from%20Singapore%20to%20Hong%20Kong.%20My%20husband%20had%20accepted%20a%20new%20role%20there%2C%20and%20after%20a%20long%20stretch%20of%20conversations%20about%20timing%2C%20family%2C%20and%20careers%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbreadwinner-taking-midlife-tech-career-break-to-find-life-purpose-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epause%20my%20career%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20follow%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20spent%20about%206%20years%20working%20in%20journalism%2C%20public%20relations%2C%20and%20marketing%20across%20Indonesia%2C%20the%20US%2C%20and%20Singapore%2C%20for%20companies%20like%20Philips%20and%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20the%20immigration%20form%20arrived%20on%20that%20flight%2C%20and%20I%20reached%20the%20line%20asking%20for%20%26quot%3BOccupation%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20expected%20my%20instincts%20to%20take%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I%20froze.%20I%20stared%20at%20the%20page%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Then%20I%20wrote%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20forced%20me%20to%20confront%20a%20question%20I%20had%20never%20really%20faced%20before%3A%20Who%20am%20I%20without%20my%20career%3F%20It%20sounds%20small%2C%20but%20for%20someone%20who%20had%20always%20tied%20my%20identity%20so%20closely%20to%20my%20work%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20quiet%20existential%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2212298324-540f-4968-9972-7920e73aa0e4%5C%22%3EI%20grew%20up%20in%20Indonesia%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20raised%20in%20Central%20Java%20by%20parents%20who%20used%20a%20simple%20philosophy%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20work%20hard%20enough%2C%20very%20little%20is%20out%20of%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20studied%20international%20relations%20at%20Arcadia%20University%20in%20Pennsylvania.%20Back%20then%2C%20my%20plan%20had%20been%20to%20become%20a%20war%20journalist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20job%2C%20a%20broadcast%20journalist%20at%20Voice%20of%20America%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20brought%20me%20close%20to%20that%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20almost%20unexpectedly%2C%20everything%20shifted.%20While%20interviewing%20Indonesia's%20trade%20minister%2C%20I%20met%20someone%20in%20her%20delegation%20who%20suggested%20I%20consider%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhottest-job-in-tech-writing-words-ai-hiring-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecareer%20in%20communications%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20conversation%20led%20me%20to%20Jakarta%20and%20quietly%20rerouted%20my%20whole%20career.%20I%20joined%20a%20global%20communications%20agency%20and%20quickly%20moved%20across%20accounts%20and%20industries%2C%20learning%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20I%20stepped%20into%20a%20leadership%20role%20at%20Philips%20Indonesia%2C%20becoming%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiscrimination-at-work-women-all-ages-jobs-hiring-employer-bosses-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eyoung%20female%20manager%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20large%2C%20male-dominated%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Singapore%2C%20continued%20in%20communications%2C%20and%20eventually%20transitioned%20into%20tech%2C%20accepting%20a%20job%20at%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pace%20was%20intense%2C%20and%20the%20learning%20curve%20steep%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20navigating%20how%20differently%20business%20culture%20and%20communication%20styles%20play%20out%20across%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeaving%20Twitter%20in%202015%20because%20of%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-for-husbands-job-left-year-later-long-distance-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehusband's%20job%20opportunity%3C%2Fa%3E%20wasn't%20easy%20%E2%80%94%20I%20had%20finally%20found%20my%20professional%20footing.%20But%20when%20my%20husband%20was%20offered%20a%20role%20in%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20we%20chose%20to%20move%20together%2C%20especially%20as%20we%20were%20thinking%20about%20starting%20a%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222635e34d-8d16-4394-82ee-ce2c998edf1e%5C%22%3EThen%2C%20life%20shifted%20again%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20three%20months%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20were%20disorienting%20in%20ways%20I%20hadn't%20anticipated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20always%20been%20defined%20by%20motion%20%E2%80%94%20teams%2C%20deadlines%2C%20decisions%2C%20output.%20Suddenly%2C%20I%20had%20none%20of%20that%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20still%20remember%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20headhunter%20who%2C%20after%20hearing%20my%20background%2C%20bluntly%20told%20me%20I%20would%20likely%20struggle%20to%20find%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-american-left-us-moved-hong-kong-job-foreigner-working-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ework%20in%20Hong%20Kong%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20neither%20a%20native%20English%20nor%20a%20Cantonese%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20come%20from%20environments%20where%20my%20voice%20was%20recognized%2C%20and%20my%20perspective%20carried%20weight%2C%20but%20in%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20I%20was%20starting%20again%20from%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221185f1ee-2d83-4307-a2a9-9e0e243a49b8%5C%22%3ESocially%2C%20I%20noticed%20a%20shift%20in%20myself%2C%20too%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20you%20do%3F%26quot%3B%2C%20I%20reached%20for%20my%20past.%20I%20would%20say%20%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20work%20for%20this%20company%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BI%20did%20this%20role%26quot%3B.%20I%20was%20constantly%20translating%20myself%20into%20something%20legible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20instinctively%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20leaning%20on%20past%20titles%20as%20a%20way%20to%20justify%20my%20place%20in%20the%20room.%20Looking%20back%2C%20it%20made%20me%20realize%20how%20quickly%20we%20can%20reduce%20people%20to%20their%20credentials%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20easily%20that%20shapes%20who%20we%20choose%20to%20listen%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20being%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20that%20experience%20changed%20something%20in%20me.%20It%20reminded%20me%20that%20value%20isn't%20tied%20to%20status%20or%20company%20names%2C%20and%20that%20everyone%20carries%20a%20story%20far%20richer%20than%20what%20appears%20on%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20team%20of%20colleagues%20at%20ByteDance.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0a8f4a94eb4c909fb2d5c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESiswoyo's%20took%20on%20roles%20at%20Uber%2C%20USAID%2C%20ByteDance%20(pictured)%2C%20and%20Netflix.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Chatrine%20Siswoyo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20volunteering%2C%20I%20met%20women%20whose%20lives%20were%20not%20defined%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompany-org-charts-most-important-people-in-tech-and-finance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecorporate%20structures%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20paper%2C%20some%20might%20have%20been%20described%20simply%20as%20%26quot%3Bhousewives.%26quot%3B%20Their%20dedication%20reminded%20me%20that%20a%20person's%20worth%20can%20never%20be%20measured%20by%20their%20title%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20time%20in%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20I%20took%20a%20short%20break%20%E2%80%94%20about%20three%20months%20%E2%80%94%20before%20returning%20to%20marketing.%20I%20quickly%20realized%20I%20needed%20to%20keep%20myself%20busy%20and%20engaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20later%20moved%20between%20Jakarta%20and%20Singapore%2C%20further%20building%20my%20career%20through%20roles%20at%20Uber%2C%20USAID%2C%20ByteDance%2C%20and%20Netflix%20over%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2254644389-6521-4252-8947-303f06049bb2%5C%22%3EThese%20days%2C%20I%20wear%20multiple%20hats%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-job-at-netflix-senior-engineer-boredom-six-figures-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20left%20Netflix%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20two%20years%2C%20and%20in%202024%2C%20I%20became%20the%20senior%20advisor%20for%20ASEAN%20at%20Vero%2C%20a%20board%20member%2C%20and%20founder%20of%20several%20charities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDo%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-corporate-job-burnout-america-live-abroad-vietnam-da-nang-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emiss%20corporate%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20I%20miss%20the%20depth%20%E2%80%94%20being%20inside%20one%20organization%20long%20enough%20to%20see%20its%20long%20arc%20unfold%20%E2%80%94%20the%20politics%2C%20the%20culture%2C%20the%20slow%20evolution%20of%20ideas%20into%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20it%20wasn't%20the%20pause%20itself%20that%20changed%20me%3B