E%3Cli%3EMeta%20has%20begun%20sending%20layoff%20emails%20to%20roughly%2010%25%20of%20its%20workforce.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20cuts%20are%20expected%20to%20eliminate%20around%208%2C000%20roles%2C%20including%20managerial%20positions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20is%20also%20shifting%20more%20than%207%2C000%20employees%20to%20AI%20initiatives.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20that%20Meta%20employees%20have%20dreaded%20for%20a%20month%20is%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmails%20have%20begun%20going%20out%20to%20roughly%2010%25%20of%20Meta's%2078%2C000%20employees%2C%20notifying%20them%20that%20they%20are%20being%20laid%20off.%20The%20notifications%20are%20being%20sent%20in%20three%20waves%20at%204%20a.m.%20local%20time%20on%20May%2020%20across%20different%20regions%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-layoffs-internal-memo-ai-job-cuts-faq-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20memo%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Meta%20HR%20chief%20Janelle%20Gale%20sent%20to%20an%20employee%20resource%20group%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20layoffs%20are%20expected%20to%20eliminate%20around%208%2C000%20roles.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20employees%20will%20receive%20a%20severance%20package%20including%2016%20weeks%20%E2%80%94%20or%20four%20months%20%E2%80%94%20in%20base%20pay%2C%20plus%20two%20weeks%20for%20every%20year%20of%20continuous%20employment%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20document%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey'll%20also%20get%2018%20months%20of%20healthcare%20coverage%20for%20themselves%20and%20their%20families%20%E2%80%94%20triple%20the%20previous%20amount%20%E2%80%94%20as%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-layoffs-hr-ceo-mark-zuckerberg-address-staff-concerns-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImpacted%20employees%20outside%20the%20US%20will%20receive%20similar%20packages%20that%20vary%20by%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFintech%20company%20Block%20recently%20gave%20recently%20laid-off%20employees%2020%20weeks%20of%20salary%20plus%20one%20additional%20week%20per%20year%20of%20tenure%20and%20six%20months%20of%20healthcare.%20Amazon%20gave%20staff%20three%20months%20of%20full%20pay%20and%20healthcare%20benefits%2C%20plus%20an%20additional%20severance%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Monday%20memo%2C%20HR%20chief%20Gale%20added%20that%20managerial%20positions%20would%20be%20cut%20across%20the%20company%20to%20create%20flatter%20organizational%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20now%20at%20the%20stage%20where%20many%20orgs%20can%20operate%20with%20a%20flatter%20structure%20with%20smaller%20teams%20of%20pods%2Fcohorts%20that%20can%20move%20faster%20and%20with%20more%20ownership%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Acrollet%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrollet%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20on%20Signal%20and%20WhatsApp%20at%20628-282-2811.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecure-news-tips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a087a56c-bbf8-4feb-910b-ffa9e93ffe82%5C%22%3EEmployees%20in%20limbo%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20an%20internal%20meeting%20last%20month%2C%20Meta's%20HR%20chief%20Janelle%20Gale%20said%20morale%20had%20taken%20a%20hit%20due%20to%20the%20looming%20layoffs%2C%20and%20that%20the%20tech%20giant%20was%20doing%20its%20best%20to%20make%20a%20%26quot%3Bshitty%26quot%3B%20situation%20%26quot%3Bthe%20best%20version%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20COBRA%20coverage%20had%20been%20tripled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Meta%20first%20announced%20the%20coming%20layoffs%20on%20April%2023%2C%20employees%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-employees-react-to-pending-job-cuts-layoffs-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20in%20a%20state%20of%20limbo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20unsure%20of%20their%20fate%20at%20the%20company.%20Meta%20said%20at%20the%20time%20in%20an%20internal%20memo%20that%20the%20job%20cuts%20would%20help%20the%20company%20run%20%26quot%3Bmore%20efficiently%26quot%3B%20and%20offset%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20also%20plans%20to%20move%20more%20than%207%2C000%20people%20to%20work%20on%20new%20initiatives%20around%20AI.%20Gale%20told%20staff%20that%20leaders%20across%20the%20company%20will%20announce%20organizational%20changes%20alongside%20the%20layoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-earnings-microsoft-ai-investment-capex-plan-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20is%20spending%20billions%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20AI%20race%20and%20in%20April%20forecast%20its%202026%20capital%20expenditures%20to%20range%20from%20%24125%20billion%20to%20%24145%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-layoffs-hr-ceo-mark-zuckerberg-address-staff-concerns-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20leaders%20told%20staff%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20are%20not%20ruling%20out%20further%20job%20cuts%20beyond%20this%20Wednesday's%2010%25%20round%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flayoff-meta-severance-details-cobra-jobs-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779247183000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0c9a18ce0a5b2f12d7d70d%3Ffo