2%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%2FO%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20year.%20This%20time%2C%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20held%20back%2C%20and%20it%20says%20a%20lot%20about%20where%20the%20company%20stands%20in%20the%20AI%20coding%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20keynote%20address%2C%20Pichai%20told%20the%20crowd%20that%20Google's%20new%20flagship%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-io-2026-gemini-3-5-pro-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGemini%203.5%20Pro%20AI%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20wasn't%20ready%20yet%2C%20drawing%20audible%20groans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20there%2C%20and%20I've%20spent%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20event%20coming%20up%20with%20a%20theory%20for%20the%20apparent%20delay%3A%20Google%20is%20holding%20this%20new%20model%20back%20for%20a%20while%20to%20get%20it%20even%20better%20at%20AI%20coding%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ai-breakthrough-vibe-coding-revolution-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaude%20Code%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20the%20world%20by%20storm%20last%20year%2C%20and%20OpenAI's%20Codex%20has%20gotten%20much%20better%20recently.%20These%20frontier%20labs%20are%20scooping%20up%20developer%20mindshare%20and%20generating%20big%20revenue%20by%20enabling%20coders%20to%20use%20AI%20tools%20with%20agents%20to%20automate%20and%20speed%20up%20coding%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20revolution%20that's%20upending%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20and%20Google%20was%20probably%20a%20bit%20behind.%20But%20not%20for%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20releasing%203.5%20Pro%2C%20Pichai%20spoke%20at%20length%20and%20with%20passion%20about%20another%20new%20model%2C%20the%20Gemini%203.5%20Flash.%20This%20is%20a%20smaller%20model%20that's%20faster%20and%20a%20lot%20cheaper%2C%20while%20being%20only%20slightly%20less%20powerful%20than%20the%20world's%20current%20top%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20has%20already%20made%203.5%20Flash%20the%20main%20model%20powering%20its%20Antigravity%20AI%20coding%20service.%20Starting%20today%2C%20software%20developers%20will%20use%20this%20tool%20to%20churn%20out%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20generate%20a%20mountain%20of%20anonymous%20and%20highly%20valuable%20data.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20an%20engineer%20starts%20a%20new%20coding%20project%20in%20Antigravity%20and%20suddenly%20halts%20the%20task%2C%20it%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esuggests%20that%20something%20in%20the%20output%20from%20Flash%203.5%20wasn't%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20can%20use%20this%20feedback%20data%20to%20improve%20the%20larger%203.5%20Pro%20model%2C%20likely%20through%20reinforcement%20learning%E2%80%94a%20technique%20in%20which%20a%20new%20AI%20model%20is%20refined%20by%20rewarding%20good%20outputs%20and%20punishing%20bad%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESignals%20from%20running%20Antigravity%20on%20the%20smaller%203.5%20Flash%20model%20will%20likely%20help%20with%20this%20process%20in%20important%20ways.%20That's%20because%20coding%20is%20particularly%20good%20at%20generating%20clear%20signals%20for%20AI%20model%20development.%20If%20the%20code%20is%20good%2C%20it%20likely%20works.%20If%20it's%20bad%2C%20it%20often%20breaks%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20should%20give%20the%20larger%203.5%20Pro%20model%20strong%20clues%20about%20which%20coding%20outputs%20worked%20and%20which%20didn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20you%20can't%20wait%20to%20get%20your%20hands%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Pichai%20said%20onstage.%20%26quot%3BGive%20us%20until%20next%20month%20to%20get%20it%20to%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20this%20big%20new%20model%20finally%20lands%2C%20I%20expect%20it%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20better%20at%20coding%20%E2%80%94%20the%20hottest%20application%20of%20generative%20AI%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsub