its%20latest%20frontier%20model%20at%20I%2FO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomewhat%20apologetically%2C%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20asked%20people%20to%20give%20Google%20until%20next%20month%20to%20deliver%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20you%20can't%20wait%20to%20get%20your%20hands%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Pichai%20said%20onstage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20industry%20is%20closely%20watching%20Google's%20big%20AI%20models%2C%20especially%20after%20Gemini%203%20outperformed%20expectations%20and%20cemented%20its%20position%20as%20an%20AI%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22161e9c3c-983a-4e35-b6ad-6ace581236cc%5C%22%3EGoogle%20burns%20through%20quadrillions%20of%20AI%20tokens%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20touted%20stunning%20numbers%20that%20showcased%20the%20rapid%20adoption%20of%20its%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20notably%2C%20Pichai%20said%20that%20people%20worldwide%20now%20burn%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogles-ceo-jokes-about-tokenmaxxing-use-of-its-ai-surges-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E3.2%20quadrillion%20AI%20tokens%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20month%20by%20using%20Google's%20products%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20seven%20times%20as%20much%20as%20last%20year.%20Many%20people's%20jaws%20literally%20dropped%20at%20the%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPichai%20bragged%20about%20other%20surging%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20Gemini%20app%20recently%20topped%20900%20million%20monthly%20active%20users%2C%20up%20more%20than%20double%20from%20400%20million%20about%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-intelligent-search-box-ai-mode-features-information-agents-io-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAI%20Overviews%20in%20Google%20Search%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20over%202.5%20billion%20monthly%20active%20users%2C%20the%20CEO%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22baeacb2e-ee61-4de8-96de-e3a8d491f138%5C%22%3EGoogle%20lags%20on%20AI%20coding%20%E2%80%94%20don't%20count%20it%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20developers%20interviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%20at%20the%20conference%20agreed%20that%20Gemini's%20coding%20abilities%20lag%20behind%20rivals%20like%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20Code%20and%20OpenAI's%20Codex.%20(None%20of%20the%20developers%20worked%20at%20Google%2C%20of%20course.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20is%20trying%20hard%20to%20catch%20up%2C%20and%20it%20could%20do%20so%20soon.%20Google%20heavily%20showcased%20Antigravity%2C%20its%20AI%20agent%20development%20product%2C%20at%20I%2FO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20models%20%26quot%3Bare%20continuing%20to%20improve%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20supercharging%20its%20coding%20abilities%20as%20well%2C%20DeepMind%20engineer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-planned-acquisition-windsurf-called-off-ceo-poached-google-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVarun%20Mohan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20cofounded%20the%20AI%20coding%20startup%20Windsurf%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20at%20the%20conference%20before%20a%20Google%20staffer%20shuffled%20him%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we're%20on%20a%20great%20track%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-io-2026-5-biggest-takeaways-ai-advances-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779235875000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0ce24a7684ba33f7380866%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-io-2026-5-biggest-takeaways-ai-advances-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20AI%20chief%20Demis%20Hassabis%20discusses%20singularity%20at%20I%2FO%202026%2C%20showcasing%20AI%20innovations%20like%20Spark%20and%20Gemini%20amid%20coding%20challenges.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22crollet%40insider.com%20(Charles%20Rollet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22c