de%20Mode%26quot%3B%20feature.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETesla%20says%20the%20driving%20mode%20works%20for%20water%20up%20to%2032%20inches%20deep%3B%20the%20lake's%20maximum%20depth%20is%20around%2065%20feet.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20read%20the%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20police%20arrested%20a%20man%20who%20they%20said%20drove%20a%20Tesla%20Cybertruck%20into%20Grapevine%20Lake%20in%20North%20Texas.%20Per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FGrapevinePolice%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGrapevine%20Police%20Department%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20man%20said%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20test%20the%20Cybertruck's%20Wade%20Mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20problem%3F%20Wade%20Mode%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Cybertruck%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tesla.com%2Fownersmanual%2Fcybertruck%2Fen_us%2FGUID-9C572163-DB86-44AC-9842-AB6EE84D6441.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eowner's%20manual%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20designed%20for%20shallow%20creeks%20or%20rivers%20that%20have%20a%20maximum%20depth%20of%2032%20inches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrapevine%20Lake%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftpwd.texas.gov%2Ffishboat%2Ffish%2Frecreational%2Flakes%2Fgrapevine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E65%20feet%20deep%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20points.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fusa.fishermap.org%2Fdepth-map%2Fgrapevine-lake%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enautical%20map%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20the%20area%20where%20the%20incident%20happened%20(Katie's%20Woods%20Park%20Boat%20Ramp%2C%20for%20curious%20locals)%2C%20the%20water%20near%20the%20shore%20is%20around%20one%20foot%20deep%20but%20quickly%20deepens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20might%20expect%2C%20the%20truck%20flooded%20and%20stopped%20working.%20The%20driver%20and%20the%20passengers%20all%20escaped%20safely%2C%20and%20the%20Cybertruck%20was%20later%20removed%20from%20the%20lake%20with%20the%20h