mpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%20TSA%20experiments%20show%20a%20new%20direction%20after%20chaos%20during%20the%20government%20shutdowns%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22TSA%20lines%20in%20Atlanta.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0cc9c0ce0a5b2f12d7d8d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20TSA%20has%20come%20up%20with%20new%20ways%20to%20try%20to%20reduce%20airport%20congestion%20after%20two%20government%20shutdowns%20strained%20the%20system.%3Cp%3EATL%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20TSA%20is%20testing%20off-site%20screening%20and%20private%20security%20after%20two%20government%20shutdowns.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThese%20signal%20the%20Trump%20Administration's%20broader%20leverage%20of%20private%20companies%20in%20aviation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECritics%20warn%20that%20privatization%20could%20introduce%20new%20security%20risks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Transportation%20Security%20Administration%20is%20rethinking%20airport%20security%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairport-security-wait-times-tsa-agent-shortage-government-shutdown-dhs-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etwo%20government%20shutdowns%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20wreaked%20havoc%20across%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20new%20initiative%2C%20TSA%20Gold%2B%2C%20aims%20to%20shift%20day-to-day%20security%20operations%20to%20private%20contractors%20without%20increasing%20airport%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20trial%2C%20launching%20in%20June%2C%20will%20allow%20some%20Boston%20airport%20passengers%20to%20clear%20security%2025%20miles%20away%2C%20then%20ride%20a%20bus%20to%20the%20airport%20for%20a%20fee%2C%20where%20they%20will%20be%20dropped%20off%20at%20their%20gates.%20It%20relies%20on%20the%20transport%20company%20Landline%20to%20keep%20the%20bus%20secure%20for%20the%20often%20over%20one-hour%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20initiatives%20have%20the%20same%20goal%3A%20Make%20airport%20security%20less%20of%20a%20headache%20for%20everyone%20and%20rely%20more%20on%20private%20companies%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20a%20new%20stance%20from%20the%20Trump%20Administration%20%E2%80%94%20privatization%20of%20aviation%20systems%20has%20been%20a%20campaign%20promise%2C%20with%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20saying%20he%20believes%20fully%20privatizing%20them%20while%20maintaining%20government%20oversight%20would%20save%20money%2C%20improve%20efficiency%2C%20and%20enhance%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20been%20experimenting%20with%20privatization%20for%20years%2C%20primarily%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthese-20-airports-dont-use-tsa-screeners-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETSA's%20Screening%20Partnership%20Program%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20uses%20contracted%20security%20officials%20to%20screen%20passengers%20and%20baggage%20at%2020%20airports%2C%20including%20San%20Francisco%20and%20Kansas%20City%2C%20as%20well%20as%20several%20smaller%20regional%20airports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20benefit%20of%20this%20became%20apparent%20in%20late%202025%20and%20early%202026%2C%20when%20thousands%20of%20federal%20TSA%20officers%20worked%20without%20pay%20during%20two%20government%20shutdowns%20after%20Congress%20failed%20to%20reach%20funding%20deals.%20Staffing%20thinned%20as%20demoralized%20workers%20called%20out%20or%20quit%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-lines-missed-flight-lost-meetings-potential-clients-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estretching%20security%20lines%20for%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20little%20to%20no%20notice.%20San%20Francisco's%20private%20security%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%20saw%20minimal%20disruptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Passengers%20line%20up%20outside%20airports.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69af34b8ccda166eed3d0b1c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPassengers%20at%20Houston%20Hobby%20Airport%20experienced%20TSA%20wait%20times%20up%20to%20three%20hours%20during%20the%20partial%20government%20shutdown.%3Cp%3EBrett%20Coomer%2FHouston%20Chronicle%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Gold%2B%2C%20officials%20want%20to%20make%20the%20Screening%20Partnership%20Program%20a%20reality%20nationwide%2C%20shifting%20not%20just%20physical%20screening%20duties%20but%20also%20equipment%20to%20contractors%20whose%20budgets%20don't%20rely%20on%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20administration%20wants%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivatizing-usps-impact-on-business-nonprofits-rural-areas-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elarger%20private%20influence%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20airport%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheldon%20Jacobson%2C%20a%20computer%20science%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Illinois%20Urbana-Champaign%20who%20helped%20regulators%20develop%20TSA%20PreCheck%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20all%20sounds%20good%2C%20with%20TSA%20setting%20the%20standards%20and%20airports%20implementing%20them.%20If%20the%20lessons%20learned%20are%20widely%20shared%2C%20there%20can%20be%20some%20benefits.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20opponents%20warn%20that%20privatizing%20airport%20security%20could%20result%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20thousands%20of%20TSA%20jobs%2C%20lower%20pay%2C%20weakened%20worker%20protections%2C%20increased%20turnover%2C%20and%20potentially%20pressure%20companies%20to%20prioritize%20profits%20over%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TSA%20employs%20roughly%2050%2C000%20security%20officers%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-agents-working-without-pay-how-much-salary-they-make-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estart%20at%20about%20%2440%2C000%20annually%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20average%20pay%20ranges%20from%20%2460%2C000%20to%20%2475%2C000%2C%20with%20higher-cost-of-living%20cities%20paying%20more.%20Experienced%20TSOs%20with%20years%20on%20the%20job%20and%20strong%20performance%20can%20advance%20into%20analytical%20and%20supervisory%20roles%20that%20make%20six%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Boston%20bus%20experiment%2C%20limited%20to%20Delta%20and%20JetBlue%20passengers%20for%20now%2C%20takes%20a%20different%20approach%20to%20involving%20private%20companies%20in%20airport%20operations%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20unusual%20idea%20comes%20with%20its%20own%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20remote%20terminal%20near%20Boston.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0cc91cbe2e5e1daf890b17%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bus%20costs%20%249%20per%20adult%2C%20while%20children%2017%20and%20under%20are%20free%2C%20and%20it's%20available%20only%20for%20Delta%20and%20JetBlue%20flights%20between%205%3A30%20am%20and%204%20pm.%20The%20ride%20can%20take%2020%20minutes%20to%20over%20an%20hour%2C%20depending%20on%20traffic.%3Cp%3EMassachusetts%20Port%20Authority%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETSA%20officers%20still%20conduct%20screening%2C%20but%20Landline%20handles%20the%20trip%20to%20the%20airport%2C%20with%20checked%20bags%20stored%20underneath%20the%20bus%20while%20passengers%20keep%20carry-ons%20and%20personal%20items%20with%20them.%20If%20Gold%2B%20succeeds%20as%20officials%20expect%2C%20it%20could%20open%20the%20door%20to%20more%20remote%20screening%20setups%20paired%20with%20private%20shuttle%20buses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJacobson%20said%20privatization%20can%20work%20%26quot%3Bso%20long%20as%20the%20standards%20for%20%5Bprivate%5D%20employees%20are%20well-defined%20and%20the%20training%20is%20rigorous%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20pilot%20bus%20program%20raises%20a%20separate%20concern%3A%20maintaining%20airport-style%20security%20outside%20the%20airport%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Landline%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bmeets%20the%20high%20security%20standards%20set%20by%20TSA%20and%20DHS.%26quot%3B%20The%20TSA%20said%20there%20will%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bmulti-layered%20screening%20of%20passengers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Jacobson%20said%20there%20are%20many%20uncontrollable%20factors%20on%20that%20trip%20to%20Logan%20%E2%80%94%20which%20will%20drive%20on%20public%20roads%20for%20sometimes%20more%20than%20an%20hour%20%E2%80%94%20pointing%20to%20the%20heightened%20risks%20when%20airport%20security%20processes%20depend%20on%20a%20separate%20operator%20outside%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-agent-government-shutdown-financial-struggle-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETSA-controlled%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20if%20the%20bus%20were%20involved%20in%20an%20accident%20or%20someone%20aboard%20got%20sick%2C%20that%20could%20compromise%20security%20and%20require%20a%20rescreening%2C%20which%20could%20cause%20travelers%20to%20miss%20their%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20see%20the%20motivation%20in%20terms%20of%20convenience%3B%20people%20still%20have%20to%20park%20at%20the%20remote%20terminal%2C%20clear%20TSA%2C%20and%20get%20on%20a%20bus%2C%26quot%3B%20Jacobson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20question%20is%2C%20will%20this%20now%20be%20a%20weak%20spot%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2-tsa-experiments-hint-trumps-move-to-privatization-airport-security-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779226321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0cc9e27684ba33f73807da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2-tsa-experiments-hint-trumps-move-to-privati